Datasets

Europeana is a database of some 30 million cultural and historical documents, images, sound and video files from Europe's museums, libraries, galleries and archives.

  • Maps and Drawings from the Catálogo Colectivo De La Red De Bibliotecas De Los Archivos Estatales

    More than 7,000 maps, city plans & architectural drawings/plans from the Catálogo Colectivo de la Red de Bibliotecas de los Archivos Estatales. The collection is a union catalog of state archives and libraries in Spain. Spanish language.

    Dataset provided by Catálogo Colectivo de la Red de Bibliotecas de los Archivos Estatales. Contact ccbae.dglab@mcu.es for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console
    Maps Architecture

  • Maps and Drawings from the Biblioteca Virtual Del Patrimonio Bibliográfico

    More than 4,000 maps and drawings from the Biblioteca Virtual del Patrimonio Bibliográfico. Spanish language.

    Dataset provided by Biblioteca Virtual del Patrimonio Bibliográfico. Contact ccbae.dglab@mcu.es for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console
    Maps Drawings

  • Drawings, Prints and Artwork from the National Library of Poland

    More than 16,000 examples of drawings, prints, artwork, posters, engravings, postcards, photographs, portraits and caricatures from the National Library of Poland. Polish language.

    Dataset provided by The National Library of Poland - Biblioteka Narodowa. Contact biblnar@bn.org.pl for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console
    Photographs Prints Drawings

  • Archaeological Artefacts from the Institute of Balkan Studies and Thracology

    500 examples of archaeological artefacts from the Institute of Balkan Studies and Thracology. Bulgarian language.

    Dataset provided by Institute of Balkan Studies and Thracology - Институт за балканистика с Център по тракология. Contact balkani@cl.bas.bg for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console
    Archaeology

  • Photographs, Prints and Posters from the Biblioteca Valenciana Digital

    More than 500 examples of photographs, prints and posters from the Biblioteca Valenciana Digital. Spanish language.

    Dataset provided by Biblioteca Valenciana Digital. Contact bivaldi@gva.es for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console
    Photographs Prints

  • Butterflies and Moths from the University of Tartu

    More than 15,000 butterflies and moths from the Natural History Museum at the University of Tartu. In English with Latin species names.

    Dataset provided by University of Tartu, Natural History Museum. Contact loodusmuuseum@ut.ee for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console

  • Fossils from the University of Tartu

    More than 9,000 fossils from the Museum of Geology, University of Tartu. In English with Latin species names.

    Dataset provided by Museum of Geology, University of Tartu. Contact mi@ut.ee for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console

  • Flowers and Trees from the Royal Botanic Garden in Edinburgh

    More than 3,000 flowers and trees from the collections of the Royal Botanic Garden in Edinburgh. In English with Latin species names.

    Dataset provided by The Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh. Contact webmaster@rbge.org.uk for more details.

    View this data in:
    Portal API Console

  • Early Photographs from the Fondo Fotográfico De La Universidad De Navarra

    More than 4,000 early photographs from 19th-century Spain in the collections of the Universidad de Navarra. Spanish language.

    Dataset provided by Fondo Fotográfico de la Universidad de Navarra. Contact dirmuseo@unav.es for more details.
